quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,WET-TINI WE EZ-ZEJTUNI
  95,2,WE TURI SININE
  95,3,WE HEDHAL-BELEDIL-’EMINI
  95,4,LEKAD HALEKNAL-’INSANE FI ‘EHSENI TEKWIMIN
  95,5,THUMME REDEDNAHU ‘ESFELE SAFILINE
  95,6,‘ILLAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI FELEHUM ‘EXHRUN GAJRU MEMNUNIN
  95,7,FEMA JUKEDHDHIBUKE BA’DU BID-DINI
  95,8,‘ELEJSEL-LAHU BI’EHKEMIL-HAKIMINE